AGI - "I cannot fail to confess that my emotion is at the limits of emotion. This is a day when affection and anxiety for what you do suddenly make sense because Caivano's challenge was one of my first major bets and government and I wasn't prepared for the emotion experienced." The President of the Council, Giorgia Meloni>, inaugurated Caivano the sports pole created in the former Delphinia. "The message is that the state can make a difference, institutions can make a difference," he said. In this place, he recalls "we start from a horror, from little girls victims, and from a failure of the institutions that here were unable to defend the weakest, the most fragile".
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
"When Don Patriciello> wrote me and told me 'Come here' I decided to do exactly this - remember the premier - on August 31 we came, we did what every citizen expects from the institutions, not limit himself to solidarity.<a href="https://www.agi.it/politica/news/2023-12-02/caivano-meloni-stupro-24259846/"> We assumed our responsibilities </a>, a challenging bet that the institutions in the past had preferred not to make. But serious politics puts things where they are difficult."&nbsp; "Here the institutions behaved as they should always behave. They realized a problem, they were called by a citizen to realize a problem, they proposed a solution, they made an announcement and that announcement did not fall into the void, that announcement has become made that citizens can see, that they can touch, that they can live and this means access to hope and it means to do it the territory in which too often the institutions thought that of hope there could not be. This is a very powerful message."&nbsp;
&nbsp;
< blockquote
"The State cannot afford free zones"
</blockquote
&nbsp;
"This nation has tolerated for too long that there were free zones and that the state was willing to back and turn the face and lower the head. We came here and said that the state could not afford it and react. And we have laid the foundations for a different story >- adds - intrigue and degradation are not a destiny, but a choice and a choice can be overturned. We are proud to have brought Caivano the hope of normal things like bringing son to play in the park."&nbsp; "We maintained the commitment - concludes Meloni, emphasizing that it delivers the sports pole on 28 May >, respecting the times announced in August 2023 - when we arrived there was only degradation and nightmare today arises a multifunctional center in which you can practice 40 sports disciplines that will be immediately operational".
&nbsp;
<div </div
<h2>"I'm that bitch of Meloni"</h2>
"President De Luca, that bitch from Meloni. How is he?" With these words the president of the Council, Giorgia Meloni, turned to the governor of the Campania Region, Vincenzo De Luca, on the occasion of the inauguration of the sports center in Caivano. Meloni then sent back to the sender the epithet with which De Luca had defined it in an outboard in Transatlantic in February last, during the protests against the differentiated autonomy of the Campania mayors in Rome.<br> In a video published by the Atreju account, with the caption 'Giorgia, teach us life', which is already widely circulating on the web, you see the premier approaching De Luca to greet him. At that point he pronounces the phrase in question. De Luca does not break out and greets her normally responding first "Welcome", then: "Good health." Meloni continues greetings with other authorities present
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
<h2 The barrel and response with De Luca</h2>
"To the president of the Region Vincenzo De Luca, who yesterday said that this was a walk of the government, I say that if all the times that the politics walk brings results like this, we would have more confidence from the citizens. We will pass again, bring this model elsewhere> we will have many other Cain, we will win the state. It is what the Italians expect from us," said Meloni, responding to the words of the president of Campania, who did not wait for the further reply: "It is necessary to take note of the beautiful, beautiful realization, but it made a wrong controversy, I never talked about walks in Cain." &nbsp;
&nbsp;
"I have not understood well what it refers to - saysDe Luca - I have never talked about walks in Caivano, so he made a completely wrong and out of context, but above all deprived of an objective reference. No one has ever talked about walks, I was allowed to take a while around yesterday Durigon - says Vincenzo De Luca - for the walk we made yesterday at the Beverello Pier. But they are government representatives who do not have much irony > and are very nervous at this time. In any case, the one to which I was referring was the walk to the Beverello pier which, as you know, is a work financed by the Gentiloni government, on request of the Campania Region - reiterates - therefore plus de souplesse, and be serene". On the work done to regenerate the sports center, De Luca expresses himself without means terms: "This is important because concrete things are worth. On concrete things and on the achievements - says the president of the Region - there is nothing but to take note and to give recognition to those who realize it".
<h2>Thanks to Don Patriciello</h2>
"Giorgia, io 'o veco e nu 'o crere. Thank you. It is "I see it and I do not believe it", in dialect, the thanks of <a href="https://www.agi.it/cronaca/news/2024-05-11/don-patriciello-de-luca-polemica-politica-26355101/"> Don Maurizio Patriciello/a>, pastor of the church of San dei santi Apostoli, to the premier Giorgia Meloni, to pore "I asked for permission to call her Giorgia," the Anticlan priest began. "Saint Augustine said that hope has two children, the first is indignation, but then we have to move forward." "Giorgia, we celebrate Easter today, but first there was the holy Friday. On July 15, 2023 I wrote to Giorgia and sent her the photos of the center built to help life, abandoned, forgotten, vandalized, unspoiled", the priest tells.
&nbsp;
"He answers me August 8: 'Sorry I see only now'; then the little girls' scempio and first again Fortuna's and before more children and murders and exterminations. On August 25 I write; 'Giorgia I have the heart torn, they are all kids, please come, make us feel Italian, come and bring the state. I would not bet a euro that 8 days after half government would come and Meloni said: 'This is free zone and should not be there'. Giorgia, I'll tell you in native speakers. Giorgia this morning or veco and nun or cred...you all take a step further."
&nbsp;
